	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The localization set that I have most often seen used by game developers was referred to as <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/FIGS" class="postlink">FIGS</a>, for French, Italian, German and Spanish, after the English original. I'm not sure to what extent there is a standard set, but this is a common one.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
